{"word":"Olives, Mount of","slug":"olives,-mount-of","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Olives, Mount of</b> Called Mount of Corruption<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Ki 23:13</a><br/> East of Jerusalem. The highway to and from the east passed over it<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=30'>2Sa 15:30</a><br/> Jesus' triumphant entry into Jerusalem by way of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=1'>Mat 21:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=11&verse=1'>Mar 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=19&verse=29'>Luk 19:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=19&verse=37'>Luk 19:37</a><br/> Jesus repairs to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=24&verse=3'>Mat 24:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=30'>Mat 26:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=13&verse=3'>Mar 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=26'>Mar 14:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=21&verse=37'>Luk 21:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=39'>Luk 22:39</a><br/> Jesus makes His ascension from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=12'>Act 1:12</a>"}]}